Mechanic Administrator - PT BAM Decorient Indonesia
Mechanic Administrator  -
Mechanic Administrator
Responsibilities
Your responsibilitiesAs Mechanic administrator, you will be responsible for creating and documenting the reports of applicating and repair/service equipment and tools (weekly/monthly report). As Mechanic administrator your main tasks and accountabilities will be:Documenting files; permit letter (in/out); equipment and tools certificates; tools inspection; etc.Creating in/out list of any type of lubricants and fuelRecording the used of water and electricianInvolve in creating the consumable stocks of equipment parts which is used in projectYour profileAs Mechanic administrator you have the following qualifications and competencies:Minimum graduate from SMA/STM/SMKUnderstand the material needs of mechanic and electricalKnow the type of lubricants and fuelUnderstand the machine of diesel fuel and its componentsInitiative, problem solver, pro-active, Integrity and culturally sensitiveProficient in Microsoft OfficeWilling to work in Cikarang area Our offer Working for BAM International means a challenging working environment where individual contributions mean a lot. We offer comprehensive training possibilities, a fitting salary and benefits package and career advancement opportunities. BAM International has an open company culture and short lines of command.Only short listed candidates will be notified for interviews
